Preserving the sanctity of what they had would mean the world not only to my mother but also to a man who‚Äôs entire being revolved around her, and her two children who are all that remains of their love. Me and Khushi have lost our mother but papa has lost his ‚ÄúJaan‚Äù. She was so much more than just an actor or a mother or a wife. She was the ultimate and the best in all these roles.
